  "page": "Hornwood",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_North.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The north and the location of Hornwood\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of Hornwood\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/300px-The_North.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/450px-The_North.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/600px-The_North.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 52.8%; left: 66.4%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 9px; font-size: 9px;\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of Hornwood\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/9px-Wolff2.PNG\" title=\"Hornwood\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/14px-Wolff2.PNG 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/18px-Wolff2.PNG 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Hornwood</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> and the location of Hornwood<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hornwood</b> is a castle in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> and the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hornwood\" title=\"House Hornwood\">House Hornwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_hornwood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_hornwood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The castle is located in the <a href=\"/index.php/Hornwood_(forest)\" title=\"Hornwood (forest)\">Hornwood forest</a> near the northwestern edge of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sheepshead_Hills\" title=\"Sheepshead Hills\">Sheepshead Hills</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> which are within the dominion of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">House Manderly</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sheepshead_hills.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_sheepshead_hills.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and the Hornwood lands also neighbor those of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">House Bolton</a> to the north.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Medrick\" title=\"Medrick\">Medrick</a> serves as maester at the castle to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Halys_Hornwood\" title=\"Halys Hornwood\">Halys Hornwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a> kidnaps and forcibly marries the widowed Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Donella_Hornwood\" title=\"Donella Hornwood\">Donella Hornwood</a>, Hornwood is <a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_in_the_Hornwood\" title=\"Fighting in the Hornwood\">seized</a> by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyman_Manderly\" title=\"Wyman Manderly\">Wyman Manderly</a> to prevent it from falling into Ramsay's hands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Davos_Seaworth\" title=\"Davos Seaworth\">Davos Seaworth</a> learns that <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> from along the <a href=\"/index.php/White_Knife\" title=\"White Knife\">White Knife</a> and Hornwood have been seeking protection at <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">Manderlys</a>. Some Hornwood men are also reported to have joined Ramsay's force marching on <a href=\"/index.php/Moat_Cailin\" title=\"Moat Cailin\">Moat Cailin</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As a condition for peace with the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>, Wyman Manderly relinquishes his claim on Hornwood lands and castles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> During the wedding of \"<a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Poole\" title=\"Jeyne Poole\">Arya Stark</a>\" to Ramsay, now legitimized as Ramsay Bolton, in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, Ramsay is introduced as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Hornwood\" title=\"Lord of the Hornwood\">Lord of the Hornwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hornwood&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_map_of_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  map of Westeros.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_hornwood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_hornwood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Hornwood.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_sheepshead_hills.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sheepshead_hills.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Sheepshead Hills.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 37\">Chapter 37</a>, The Prince of Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 28\">Chapter 28</a>, Bran IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Davos II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 19\">Chapter 19</a>, Davos III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_North\" title=\"Template:Region North\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Region_North&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Region North (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Region_North&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThe <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Settlements</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Barrow_Hall\" title=\"Barrow Hall\">Barrow Hall</a></li>\n<l